{"article_id":"OCIvseB5AXR2pxY7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"DES MOINES , Iowa -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Hillary Clinton sought to minimize new disclosures","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that top secret government information passed through the private email server","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"she used","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"when she was secretary of state ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"dismissing the controversy as an \" inter-agency dispute \"","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that pales next to the larger issues on the minds of voters .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"In an interview with NBC News on Saturday morning , two days before the Iowa caucuses , Mrs. Clinton said ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"\" It ' s the same story","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that ' s been going on for months now .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"And I just don ' t think","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"most people are as concerned about that","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"as they are about what we ' re going to do","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"to get the economy going . \"","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"The State Department on Friday said","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"it was withholding in their entirety 22 documents from an archive of Mrs. Clinton ' s emails","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"being publicly released ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"they contained material so sensitive","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that it could not even be shared in redacted form .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"The department also said","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"it was opening an investigation","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"into whether the emails were classified at the time","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"they were sent or received .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Officials have previously said","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"the redactions in the roughly 43,000 pages of her emails","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"so far released","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"were made for information","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that was classified only after the fact .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Mrs. Clinton ' s exclusive use of a private email account and a server","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"kept at her home Chappaqua , N.Y. ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"has weighed on her campaign","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"since she entered the race last April .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Her refusal","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to use the standard-issue government account","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"has fueled perceptions","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"that she is secretive in her dealings","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and wanted to shield her communications from public records requests .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Mrs. Clinton has denied such charges ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"she merely wanted the \" convenience \"","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"of using a single device","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"rather than carrying one for work and another for personal correspondence .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"She has also said","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"she never sent or received any emails","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"marked classified at the time .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"What is happening ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"she said ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"is different federal agencies are arguing among themselves","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"about whether certain information in her email records was classified .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"The FBI is looking into her email arrangement","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"and Republican critics have said","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"she should face legal consequences for what they say","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"was an unconventional email practice","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"that put government secrets at risk .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"The Republican National Committee , in a statement Friday , said","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"that \" any doubt","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"about whether Clinton discussed some of the government ' s most highly classified information on her secret email server","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"can now be cast aside . \"","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"In the NBC News interview , Mrs. Clinton said ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"\" I ' m really not concerned . \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"\" This doesn ' t change anything about the fundamental facts , \"","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"\" I never sent or received any email","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"marked ' classified. '","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"I take classified information very seriously .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"I want to get things out","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"and I want to people to understand","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"based on what happened","depth":16},{"id":69,"text":"and when it was happening in real time","depth":17},{"id":70,"text":"there were no classification markings ,","depth":17},{"id":71,"text":"and that ' s what you have to be guided by . \"","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"State Department Says","depth":4},{"id":73,"text":"22 Clinton Emails Are Too Classified to Release","depth":4},{"id":74,"text":"Who Will Win the Iowa Caucus ?","depth":4},{"id":75,"text":"It Depends on Who Shows Up At Trump Rallies ,","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Buttons","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Promising Death to ISIS and Prison to Clinton","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Sell Briskly","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":157,"left":0,"right":156,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":149,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":91,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":84,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":82,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":1,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":2,"right":80,"relati